# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-04-15 14:25

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:7
translate spanish day0_2a8ebe20:

    # "It has been a few days since I've' checked my e-mail."
    "Han pasado unos días desde que revisé mi correo electrónico."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:10
translate spanish day0_6ea4ba89:

    # "As soon as I see the message sitting in my inbox, I feel in my gut that something is wrong."
    "En cuanto veo el mensaje en mi bandeja de entrada, siento en lo más profundo de mi ser que algo va mal."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:14
translate spanish day0_9bd314a2:

    # "Dad is missing? Disappeared? What does that even mean?"
    "¿Papá está desaparecido? ¿Ha desaparecido? ¿Qué significa eso siquiera?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:15
translate spanish day0_79ff2c19:

    # "I try to call Lisa, but the phone is disconnected. I e-mail back, but don't get a reply."
    "Intento llamar a Lisa, pero el teléfono está desconectado. Le respondo por correo electrónico, pero no obtengo respuesta."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:16
translate spanish day0_af17984d:

    # "I need to go home."
    "Tengo que ir a casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:25
translate spanish day0_a3b78350:

    # "TWO DAYS LATER"
    "DOS DÍAS DESPUÉS"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:28
translate spanish day0_030e178d:

    # "The Uber driver pulls up in front of my family's house – the house I had grown up in."
    "El conductor de Uber se detiene frente a la casa de mi familia, la casa en la que crecí."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:29
translate spanish day0_949b7226:

    # "I've only been away for three years, but it feels like a lifetime. I barely remember the place, and the things I do remember feel like they had happened to somebody else – like I had dreamed them or seen them in a movie."
    "Solo he estado fuera tres años, pero me parece toda una vida. Apenas recuerdo el lugar, y las cosas que recuerdo parecen haberle pasado a otra persona, como si las hubiera soñado o visto en una película."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:32
translate spanish day0_c142ebfa:

    # "After Mom died, my dad had moved us into this house. It was ten years later that he started dating Lisa and she moved in with us, along with her daughter Suzy."
    "Después de que mamá muriera, mi padre nos mudó a esta casa. Diez años más tarde empezó a salir con Lisa y ella se mudó con nosotros, junto con su hija Suzy."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:33
translate spanish day0_4b89f1ac:

    # "Then I moved away a year after that to go to college in Brazil – as far away from this place as I could possibly get."
    "Luego me mudé un año después para ir a la universidad en Brasil, lo más lejos posible de este lugar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:34
translate spanish day0_5d54d54c:

    # "I didn't leave under the best circumstances either."
    "Tampoco me fui en las mejores circunstancias."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:35
translate spanish day0_8f36008b:

    # "It felt like Dad was trying to replace Mom. I know now that I had been acting ridiculous, but I'd said some things that I regret, and I still haven't apologized for it."
    "Sentía que papá estaba intentando sustituir a mamá. Ahora sé que me comporté de forma ridícula, pero dije algunas cosas de las que me arrepiento, y todavía no me he disculpado por ello."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:36
translate spanish day0_dcd0e6e9:

    # "And now my dad is missing, and I may never be able to apologize to him."
    "Y ahora mi padre ha desaparecido, y puede que nunca pueda pedirle perdón."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:37
translate spanish day0_e04098c7:

    # "I need to know what's going on. Step one of that is talking to Lisa."
    "Necesito saber qué está pasando. El primer paso es hablar con Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:38
translate spanish day0_ae22b1fe:

    # pc "Thanks for the ride."
    pc "Gracias por traerme."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:39
translate spanish day0_6b2c2e0d:

    # "Uber Driver" "No problem. Good luck with your dad."
    "Uber Driver" "No hay problema. Buena suerte con tu padre."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:42
translate spanish day0_bd06bca7:

    # "I step out of the car, pulling my suitcase behind me – all of my possessions hastily stuffed inside before leaving college and coming home."
    "Salgo del coche, arrastrando mi maleta detrás de mí: todas mis pertenencias metidas a toda prisa dentro antes de dejar la universidad y volver a casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:43
translate spanish day0_ee16e2af:

    # "The Uber Driver gives me a wave before driving away, leaving me standing in the driveway alone."
    "El conductor de Uber me dice adiós con la mano antes de alejarse, dejándome solo en la entrada."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:44
translate spanish day0_1d05517b:

    # "The curtain in the front room moves to the side and a shadowed face looks out at me through the dusty glass."
    "La cortina del salón se corre hacia un lado y un rostro en penumbra me mira a través del cristal polvoriento."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:45
translate spanish day0_ffa819f6:

    # "A moment later, the front door opens with a creak."
    "Un momento después, la puerta principal se abre con un chirrido."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:49
translate spanish day0_b886cbad:

    # sp "[pcname]?"
    sp "[pcname]?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:50
translate spanish day0_1dce07cb:

    # pc "Hey Lisa."
    pc "Hola, Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:51
translate spanish day0_c451ce54:

    # sp "Oh my God, I can't believe you're here."
    sp "Dios mío, no puedo creer que estés aquí."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:54
translate spanish day0_4794e2ea:

    # "She rushes out of the house and across the lawn towards me, throwing her arms around my back and pulling me into a hug, sobbing lightly against my shoulder."
    "Sale corriendo de la casa y cruza el jardín hacia mí, echándome los brazos al cuello y abrazándome, sollozando ligeramente contra mi hombro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:55
translate spanish day0_168a1c2d:

    # "Then she pulls away, tears still in her eyes."
    "Luego se separa, con lágrimas aún en los ojos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:59
translate spanish day0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/lisa_sorry3.wav'
    voice 'voices/lisa_sorry3.wav'

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:60
translate spanish day0_b4977ec9:

    # sp "I'm sorry, it's just so good to see you again."
    sp "Lo siento, es que me alegro tanto de volver a verte."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:61
translate spanish day0_ef7640f1:

    # sp "I didn't know if you got my e-mail or not."
    sp "No sabía si habías recibido mi correo electrónico o no."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:62
translate spanish day0_c351ff73:

    # pc "I tried to call you and message you back, but couldn't get through."
    pc "Intenté llamarte y responderte, pero no conseguí contactar contigo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:63
translate spanish day0_ab5c6be7:

    # sp "I didn't have enough money to keep paying the phone bill, or the internet. I used Suzy's phone to send that message."
    sp "No tenía suficiente dinero para seguir pagando la factura del teléfono ni de Internet. Usé el teléfono de Suzy para enviarte ese mensaje."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:64
translate spanish day0_4aaf53f0:

    # sp "Why don't you come inside? Your room is still just like you left it. "
    sp "¿Por qué no entras? Tu habitación sigue tal y como la dejaste."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:65
translate spanish day0_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "Vale."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:68
translate spanish day0_f0440310:

    # "I look up at the house one more time, hesitating for some reason. "
    "Miro la casa una vez más, dudando por alguna razón."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:69
translate spanish day0_c19f0382:

    # "Everything feels so awkward. Like seeing an old friend that you hadn't talked to since high school after you had both grown up and gone in completely different directions, became different people."
    "Todo me resulta tan incómodo. Como ver a una vieja amiga con la que no habías hablado desde el instituto, después de que ambas hubierais crecido y tomado caminos completamente diferentes, convirtiéndoos en personas distintas."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:70
translate spanish day0_521dbb9a:

    # "Lisa waits at the door expectantly."
    "Lisa espera en la puerta con expectación."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:73
translate spanish day0_44deb548:

    # sp "Come on."
    sp "Vamos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:74
translate spanish day0_7ef33df2:

    # "I follow her inside."
    "La sigo al interior."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:78
translate spanish day0_cb8b4dc4:

    # "The house isn't much different than I remembered. Some new decorations, but a lot of the old stuff is still there too."
    "La casa no ha cambiado mucho de lo que recordaba. Hay algunos adornos nuevos, pero muchas de las cosas antiguas siguen ahí también."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:80
translate spanish day0_f76dd47c:

    # "A doorway to the right leads to the kitchen, with the always-clean white cabinets and wooden countertops."
    "Una puerta a la derecha conduce a la cocina, con los armarios blancos siempre limpios y las encimeras de madera."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:83
translate spanish day0_5f5c5eda:

    # "To the left, another doorway goes into the living room, where there are a couple of sofas and a television mounted on the wall across from them."
    "A la izquierda, otra puerta da al salón, donde hay un par de sofás y un televisor colgado en la pared frente a ellos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:84
translate spanish day0_7532ecd1:

    # "The furniture is different, the television upgraded, but the photos on the wall are exactly the same as I remember them three years ago."
    "Los muebles son diferentes, la televisión es más moderna, pero las fotos de la pared son exactamente las mismas que recuerdo de hace tres años."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:85
translate spanish day0_62149b84:

    # "Pictures of me mostly, along with others of my dad and Lisa, a few of Suzy, and even some of my mom."
    "En su mayoría son fotos mías, junto con otras de mi padre y Lisa, algunas de Suzy e incluso algunas de mi madre."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:89
translate spanish day0_dcb39111:

    # "Directly in front of me are the stairs leading up to the second floor, while the hall going past the stairs leads to the door that goes down into the basement where Dad's office is."
    "Justo delante de mí están las escaleras que suben al segundo piso, mientras que el pasillo que pasa junto a las escaleras conduce a la puerta que baja al sótano, donde está el despacho de papá."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:90
translate spanish day0_a1a128e4:

    # "There's police tape over the door. I'll have to ask Lisa about that."
    "Hay cinta policial sobre la puerta. Tendré que preguntarle a Lisa qué pasa con eso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:91
translate spanish day0_f27132b3:

    # "Past that, the door to the right goes to the master bedroom and bathroom and the door to the left leads to the laundry room. Then there's a patio door in the back that opens into the back yard."
    "Más allá de ahí, la puerta de la derecha da al dormitorio principal y al baño, y la de la izquierda lleva al lavadero. Luego hay una puerta acristalada en la parte trasera que da al jardín trasero."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:94
translate spanish day0_1758423e:

    # pc "What's the deal with the police tape?"
    pc "¿Qué pasa con la cinta policial?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:95
translate spanish day0_3089e2b3:

    # sp "Oh, they don't want anybody down there until they get finished going through some of the things that they took."
    sp "Ah, no quieren que nadie baje ahí hasta que terminen de revisar algunas de las cosas que se llevaron."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:96
translate spanish day0_78bdaf37:

    # sp "The detective locked the door and took the key with her."
    sp "La detective cerró la puerta con llave y se llevó la llave."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:97
translate spanish day0_c627e703:

    # pc "Wow. Okay."
    pc "Vaya. Vale."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:98
translate spanish day0_fec9a6b1:

    # sp "You can go put your bag in your room if you want. I was just finishing up dinner."
    sp "Puedes ir a dejar la maleta en tu habitación si quieres. Justo estaba terminando de preparar la cena."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:99
translate spanish day0_aef6c125:

    # pc "Oh, don't worry about it. I can just get take-out or something. I know you weren't really prepared for me coming today."
    pc "Oh, no te preocupes. Puedo pedir comida para llevar o algo así. Sé que no estabas preparada para que viniera hoy."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:100
translate spanish day0_c773dfdd:

    # sp "Nonsense. I made chicken fried steak. There's plenty."
    sp "Tonterías. He hecho filete de pollo frito. Hay de sobra."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:101
translate spanish day0_18768229:

    # "Chicken fried steak does sound delicious."
    "El filete de pollo frito suena delicioso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:102
translate spanish day0_05d61a38:

    # pc "Okay, I'll just go put these up."
    pc "Vale, voy a guardar esto."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:105
translate spanish day0_00910cb6:

    # sp "Sounds good. Make yourself comfortable. Suzy will be home soon. I'm sure she'll be excited to see you."
    sp "Suena bien. Ponte cómoda. Suzy llegará pronto. Seguro que se alegrará de verte."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:106
translate spanish day0_54c86bd6:

    # "I doubt that. Suzy and I had never really gotten along. I think that she's always been jealous of me, because I'm older and always got to do more interesting things than she did."
    "Lo dudo. Suzy y yo nunca nos hemos llevado bien. Creo que siempre ha estado celosa de mí, porque soy mayor y siempre he hecho cosas más interesantes que ella."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:107
translate spanish day0_f84afb0d:

    # "She seems so stuck-up to me. Like she and Lisa are just so much better than me and Dad."
    "A mí me parece tan estirada. Como si ella y Lisa fueran mucho mejores que papá y yo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:108
translate spanish day0_1fb90770:

    # "That was three years ago though, I had to remind myself. People can change. I know I have. Although returning to this place is making old feelings return as well."
    "Aunque eso fue hace tres años, tuve que recordarme a mí misma. La gente puede cambiar. Sé que yo lo he hecho. Aunque volver a este lugar también está haciendo que resurjan viejos sentimientos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:109
translate spanish day0_d7c1e2c2:

    # "I need to try to give them a chance. To start over. I need to be nice. It would be good for me and for the entire family."
    "Tengo que intentar darles una oportunidad. Empezar de nuevo. Tengo que ser amable. Sería bueno para mí y para toda la familia."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:112
translate spanish day0_6834d5ee:

    # "I take my bag up the stairs. My door is to the left, while Suzy's door, which she painted as soon as she moved into the house, is to the right."
    "Subo mi bolsa por las escaleras. Mi puerta está a la izquierda, mientras que la de Suzy, que pintó nada más mudarse a la casa, está a la derecha."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:113
translate spanish day0_c3457fef:

    # "I open my bedroom door and walk inside."
    "Abro la puerta de mi habitación y entro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:116
translate spanish day0_e134735d:

    # "All my junk that had been lying around the room when I left is all put away now, but the decorations are exactly how I had left them."
    "Todas mis cosas que estaban tiradas por la habitación cuando me fui están ahora guardadas, pero la decoración está exactamente como la dejé."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:117
translate spanish day0_81daa922:

    # "Band, movie, and video game posters on the walls. My old laptop and computer desk are in the corner covered in a thin layer of dust."
    "Pósters de bandas, películas y videojuegos en las paredes. Mi viejo portátil y el escritorio del ordenador están en la esquina, cubiertos por una fina capa de polvo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:118
translate spanish day0_d3121b8d:

    # "My Queen-sized bed is in the other corner, made up as if it were waiting for me. My nightstand next to it still has my favorite lamp on it as well."
    "Mi cama de matrimonio está en la otra esquina, hecha como si me estuviera esperando. En la mesita de noche que hay junto a ella sigue estando mi lámpara favorita."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:119
translate spanish day0_5c2ab389:

    # "I look around at the posters and can't help but laugh at myself. I had thought this stuff was so cool. I hadn't even realized how much I'd changed over the few years I'd been away from Skyhill."
    "Miro los pósters a mi alrededor y no puedo evitar reírme de mí misma. Pensaba que todo esto era genial. Ni siquiera me había dado cuenta de lo mucho que había cambiado en los pocos años que había estado lejos de Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:120
translate spanish day0_ef69d95d:

    # "I shake my head and put my bag on the dresser nearby that is still full of my clothes that I'd left behind when I moved."
    "Niego con la cabeza y dejo mi bolsa en la cómoda cercana, que todavía está llena de la ropa que dejé atrás cuando me mudé."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:121
translate spanish day0_31c8b952:

    # "I shuffle through some of the clothing before deciding that all this stuff is going to have to get donated. I won't be caught dead wearing these clothes again."
    "Reviso un poco la ropa antes de decidir que todo esto va a tener que ser donado. Ni loca volvería a ponerme esta ropa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:122
translate spanish day0_f0fd0cf7:

    # "If I'm going to stay here for any length of time, the decorations on the wall have to change too."
    "Si voy a quedarme aquí por un tiempo, la decoración de la pared también tiene que cambiar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:123
translate spanish day0_6548a872:

    # "I'm not into these bands at all anymore. Hell, most of them aren't together anymore and the lead singer in that one is in jail over sexual assault charges."
    "Ya no me gustan nada estos grupos. Joder, la mayoría ya ni siquiera existen y el cantante de ese está en la cárcel acusado de agresión sexual."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:124
translate spanish day0_f45d7436:

    # "I walk over to that poster and rip it down, ball it up, and toss it into the garbage can."
    "Me acerco a ese póster, lo arranco, lo hago una bola y lo tiro al cubo de la basura."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:125
translate spanish day0_daf8f563:

    # pc "Screw it."
    pc "Que le den."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:126
translate spanish day0_1153338c:

    # "I rip the rest of them down too. I need a new start. I'm not the same person that I had been when I lived here before and liked this stuff. I've changed and everything else needs to change too."
    "Arranco el resto también. Necesito un nuevo comienzo. No soy la misma persona que era cuando vivía aquí antes y me gustaban estas cosas. He cambiado y todo lo demás también tiene que cambiar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:129
translate spanish day0_11cc59ea:

    # "When I've finished, a couple minutes later, the walls are bare and the trash can is full. I'll redecorate later, if I decide to stay."
    "Cuando termino, un par de minutos más tarde, las paredes están desnudas y el cubo de la basura está lleno. Redecoraré más tarde, si decido quedarme."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:133
translate spanish day0_c85d2e30:

    # "I take the bag out of the trash can and carry it down the stairs, heading towards the back door where I know the outdoor bins are kept."
    "Saco la bolsa del cubo de la basura y la llevo bajando las escaleras, dirigiéndome hacia la puerta trasera, donde sé que están los contenedores de la calle."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:134
translate spanish day0_c7469e66:

    # "I'd done this same routine every week growing up. Taking out the garbage was always one of the chores that I did for my weekly $20 allowance."
    "De pequeño hacía esta misma rutina todas las semanas. Sacar la basura siempre fue una de las tareas que hacía a cambio de mi paga semanal de 20 dólares."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:135
translate spanish day0_b9ad02f6:

    # "Lisa calls from the kitchen as I pass."
    "Lisa me llama desde la cocina al pasar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:136
translate spanish day0_15b806ca:

    # sp "Where are you going? Not leaving already are you?"
    sp "¿A dónde vas? ¿No te irás ya, verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:137
translate spanish day0_b5e60a63:

    # pc "Just taking out the garbage. I'll be right back."
    pc "Solo voy a sacar la basura. Vuelvo enseguida."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:138
translate spanish day0_c85b3c7e:

    # "I walk past the basement door, past the door leading into my dad's and Lisa's room, and out the back door."
    "Paso por delante de la puerta del sótano, de la puerta que da a la habitación de mi padre y de Lisa, y salgo por la puerta trasera."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:141
translate spanish day0_f2d37ac4:

    # "The back yard is a mess. One of the fence pickets is down, there are patches of weeds everywhere, and the grass is up past my knees, as if nobody has mowed it in months."
    "El patio trasero es un desastre. Uno de los palos de la valla está caído, hay matas de malas hierbas por todas partes y la hierba me llega por encima de las rodillas, como si nadie la hubiera cortado en meses."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:142
translate spanish day0_f94bb3ce:

    # "I walk around to where the trashcans are, behind the garage. They're overflowing with garbage as if somebody had forgotten to take them out to the curb last week... and maybe the week before that as well."
    "Doy la vuelta hasta donde están los cubos de basura, detrás del garaje. Están desbordados de basura, como si alguien se hubiera olvidado de sacarlos a la acera la semana pasada... y quizá también la semana anterior."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:143
translate spanish day0_12d3e32e:

    # "I sit the trash bag on top of the bin, making a mental note to ask when trash pick-up is, so that I can be sure to get it out. "
    "Dejo la bolsa de basura encima del cubo y tomo nota mentalmente de preguntar cuándo recogen la basura, para asegurarme de sacarla. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:144
translate spanish day0_734ac1ca:

    # "I guess Lisa has been a bit distracted with my missing dad."
    "Supongo que Lisa ha estado un poco distraída con la desaparición de mi padre."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:145
translate spanish day0_0a4deb90:

    # "???" "[pcname]? Is that you?"
    "???" "[pcname]? ¿Eres tú?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:150
translate spanish day0_13302e89:

    # "I look over to where the voice came from and see a face watching me through the gap in the wooden fence on the other side of the yard."
    "Miro hacia donde viene la voz y veo una cara que me observa a través del hueco de la valla de madera al otro lado del jardín."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:151
translate spanish day0_82512aa5:

    # pc "Jamie?"
    pc "¿Jamie?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:152
translate spanish day0_c324c938:

    # "Jamie had been my neighbor for years growing up. We played together in the yard when we were young and were good friends all the way through junior high."
    "Jamie había sido mi vecina durante años mientras crecíamos. Jugábamos juntas en el jardín cuando éramos pequeñas y fuimos buenas amigas durante toda la secundaria."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:153
translate spanish day0_66d7d185:

    # "Then we started hanging out with different crowds when we went to high school and never really kept up with each other after that, aside from nods as we passed in the hall."
    "Luego empezamos a salir con grupos diferentes cuando fuimos al instituto y nunca volvimos a estar en contacto después de eso, aparte de saludarnos con un gesto cuando nos cruzábamos en el pasillo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:154
translate spanish day0_d75b5d1b:

    # "I walk through the overgrown grass to the fence to talk to her."
    "Camino por la hierba crecida hasta la valla para hablar con ella."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:158
translate spanish day0_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_001.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_001.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:159
translate spanish day0_c579b7b0:

    # gnd "I'm surprised you remembered my name."
    gnd "Me sorprende que te acuerdes de mi nombre."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:160
translate spanish day0_59b86f08:

    # pc "We were friends for years, Jamie! I'm not going to forget your name. How have you been?"
    pc "¡Fuimos amigos durante años, Jamie! No voy a olvidar tu nombre. ¿Cómo te ha ido?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:163
translate spanish day0_21d6813b:

    # gnd "Oh, pretty good. You know, just going to college and still living here."
    gnd "Oh, bastante bien. Ya sabes, voy a la universidad y sigo viviendo aquí."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:164
translate spanish day0_975b1fd3:

    # gnd "What about you? I thought you were going to school in Brazil or something?"
    gnd "¿Y tú? Creía que ibas a estudiar a Brasil o algo así."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:165
translate spanish day0_a95318dd:

    # pc "I was. I finished my third year there and was planning on staying to graduate, but this stuff with my dad happened."
    pc "Así era. Terminé mi tercer año allí y pensaba quedarme para graduarme, pero pasó lo de mi padre."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:168
translate spanish day0_e16cc8f9:

    # gnd "Oh yeah, I heard about that. They still don't know what happened to him?"
    gnd "Ah, sí, me enteré de eso. ¿Todavía no saben qué le pasó?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:169
translate spanish day0_35917d41:

    # pc "I don't think so. I just got here and haven't really started looking into it. Trying to settle in first, you know?"
    pc "No lo creo. Acabo de llegar y aún no he empezado a investigar. Primero intento instalarme, ¿sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:170
translate spanish day0_58eca7fc:

    # gnd "I understand."
    gnd "Lo entiendo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:171
translate spanish day0_78191689:

    # "We stand there for a moment in awkward silence. It's hard to have a normal conversation with the cloud of my missing father looming over our heads."
    "Nos quedamos allí un momento en un silencio incómodo. Es difícil mantener una conversación normal con la sombra de la desaparición de mi padre cerniéndose sobre nuestras cabezas."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:174
translate spanish day0_8fa47015:

    # gnd "We should go grab a coffee sometime and catch up."
    gnd "Deberíamos ir a tomar un café algún día y ponernos al día."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:182
translate spanish neighborsure_eb2314d3:

    # pc "Sure, I'd like that."
    pc "Claro, me encantaría."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:186
translate spanish neighborsure_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_002.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_002.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:187
translate spanish neighborsure_59e12605:

    # gnd "Great! I'm looking forward to it."
    gnd "¡Genial! Estoy deseándolo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:188
translate spanish neighborsure_616126a9:

    # gnd "Let me give you my phone number."
    gnd "Déjame darte mi número de teléfono."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:189
translate spanish neighborsure_ec3ea59f:

    # pc "Well, I don't have a phone right now. I sort of left in a hurry and forgot the thing in Brazil. I even had to call an Uber from a pay phone."
    pc "Bueno, ahora mismo no tengo teléfono. Me fui un poco a toda prisa y me lo olvidé en Brasil. Incluso tuve que llamar a un Uber desde una cabina."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:190
translate spanish neighborsure_4d9a5c08:

    # gnd "Wow, I didn't even know you could do that."
    gnd "Vaya, ni siquiera sabía que se podía hacer eso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:191
translate spanish neighborsure_07ae5ff4:

    # gnd "Well, you know where I live anyways. Just come over and see me sometime."
    gnd "Bueno, de todas formas ya sabes dónde vivo. Pásate a verme algún día."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:192
translate spanish neighborsure_bf344fc1:

    # pc "I'll be sure to do that."
    pc "Lo haré sin falta."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:193
translate spanish neighborsure_3ea1fb42:

    # gnd "Okay, I'll let you get back to what you were doing. It's really good to see you again, [pcname]."
    gnd "Vale, te dejo que sigas con lo que estabas haciendo. Me alegro mucho de volver a verte, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:194
translate spanish neighborsure_b59564bf:

    # pc "Good to see you too. Talk to you later."
    pc "Yo también me alegro de verte. Hablamos luego."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:195
translate spanish neighborsure_53dafd04:

    # "She smiles and gives me a wave before turning around and walking back inside her house."
    "Sonríe y me dice adiós con la mano antes de darse la vuelta y volver a entrar en su casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:200
translate spanish neighborbusy_af2bb653:

    # "She is unable to hide the disappointment on her face."
    "No puede ocultar la decepción en su rostro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:202
translate spanish neighborbusy_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_003.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_003.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:203
translate spanish neighborbusy_34e40ec9:

    # gnd "Oh, okay."
    gnd "Ah, vale."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:204
translate spanish neighborbusy_1708b5ad:

    # gnd "Well, if you change your mind, you know where I live."
    gnd "Bueno, si cambias de opinión, ya sabes dónde vivo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:205
translate spanish neighborbusy_994698a4:

    # gnd "I'll let you get back to what you were doing. It was nice to see you again."
    gnd "Te dejo seguir con lo que estabas haciendo. Me ha encantado volver a verte."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:208
translate spanish neighborbusy_4d48c356:

    # "She puts on an obviously fake smile and gives me a short wave before quickly turning around and walking back inside her house."
    "Esboza una sonrisa claramente falsa y me saluda con la mano brevemente antes de darse la vuelta rápidamente y volver a entrar en su casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:215
translate spanish dinner_6bf7ca74:

    # "I hear a car pull into the driveway and the door shut. Must be Suzy."
    "Oigo un coche entrar en el camino de acceso y la puerta cerrarse. Debe de ser Suzy."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:216
translate spanish dinner_15d46ed4:

    # "It's a bit strange to think of her driving. She'd been fifteen years old when I left and most of the time I had to drive her everywhere."
    "Me resulta un poco extraño imaginarla conduciendo. Tenía quince años cuando me fui y, la mayor parte del tiempo, tenía que llevarla yo a todas partes."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:217
translate spanish dinner_0530e225:

    # "Now, I might need her to drive me. Until I can get a car at least. How the hell am I going to get a car?"
    "Ahora, puede que sea ella quien tenga que llevarme a mí. Al menos hasta que consiga un coche. ¿Cómo demonios voy a conseguir un coche?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:223
translate spanish dinner_a0b77eb0:

    # "I walk back inside and see Lisa and Suzy standing at the front door. Suzy looks over at me with an expression that I can't decipher."
    "Vuelvo a entrar y veo a Lisa y a Suzy de pie junto a la puerta principal. Suzy me mira con una expresión que no logro descifrar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:224
translate spanish dinner_536ca09a:

    # "Is she happy to see me, or upset, or just surprised?"
    "¿Está contenta de verme, molesta o simplemente sorprendida?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:225
translate spanish dinner_b9a34438:

    # "She looks a lot different than the last time I had seen her. Not a child anymore. All grown up."
    "Se ve muy diferente a la última vez que la vi. Ya no es una niña. Está toda crecida."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:249
translate spanish dinner_b9085ed0:

    # sp "There he is now."
    sp "Ahí está."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:250
translate spanish dinner_f3bfb9f9:

    # pc "Hey, [sis]."
    pc "Hola, [sis]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:254
translate spanish dinner_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/suzy_hey1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/suzy_hey1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:255
translate spanish dinner_f4685411:

    # ss "Hey."
    ss "Hola."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:258
translate spanish dinner_266752d5:

    # "She turns back towards Lisa."
    "Se vuelve hacia Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:259
translate spanish dinner_099bdf34:

    # ss "So what's for dinner?"
    ss "¿Qué hay para cenar?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:262
translate spanish dinner_6adaf09c:

    # sp "That's it? Hey, what's for dinner?"
    sp "¿Eso es todo? Oye, ¿qué hay para cenar?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:263
translate spanish dinner_d377dbd3:

    # sp "You haven't seen [pcname] in three years. At least give him a hug or something."
    sp "No has visto a [pcname] en tres años. Al menos dale un abrazo o algo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:266
translate spanish dinner_7d526f5b:

    # ss "Do you want a hug, [bro]?"
    ss "¿Quieres un abrazo, [bro]?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:273
translate spanish hugno_1843469a:

    # pc "I mean you don't have to."
    pc "Quiero decir que no tienes por qué."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:275
translate spanish hugno_67e29172:

    # ss "Good. I smell dinner. Let's eat, I'm starving!"
    ss "Bien. Huelo la cena. ¡Vamos a comer, me muero de hambre!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:279
translate spanish hugno_73d3290c:

    # sp "Suzy!"
    sp "¡Suzy!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:280
translate spanish hugno_6f0bb30f:

    # ss "He said I don't have to. Not everybody is a hugger mom. Respect people's boundaries."
    ss "Ha dicho que no tengo por qué. No todo el mundo es de los que dan abrazos, mamá. Respeta los límites de la gente."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:281
translate spanish hugno_672d419d:

    # sp "I can't believe you."
    sp "No me lo puedo creer."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:284
translate spanish hugyes_0fdda645:

    # pc "We probably should, right?"
    pc "Probablemente deberíamos, ¿no?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:287
translate spanish hugyes_b52b7bc9:

    # ss "I guess."
    ss "Supongo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:291
translate spanish hugyes_627ce8ab:

    # "She hesitantly walks towards me and lightly puts her arms around me, barely touching."
    "Se acerca a mí con vacilación y me rodea ligeramente con los brazos, sin apenas tocarme."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:292
translate spanish hugyes_e1fa87a8:

    # pc "It's good to see you, [sis]."
    pc "Me alegro de verte, [sis]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:293
translate spanish hugyes_3caba330:

    # ss "Good to see you too."
    ss "Yo también me alegro de verte."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:294
translate spanish hugyes_a2f7fa6a:

    # "Then she quickly pulls away."
    "Luego se aparta rápidamente."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:300
translate spanish hugyes_78d5d1d8:

    # ss "Alright, we hugged, let's eat, I'm starving!"
    ss "Vale, ya nos hemos abrazado, ¡vamos a comer, me muero de hambre!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:305
translate spanish dinner2_4f4f66ba:

    # "We make our plates in the kitchen and bring them to the small four-person table in the dining room."
    "Preparamos los platos en la cocina y los llevamos a la mesita de cuatro personas del comedor."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:306
translate spanish dinner2_a501017d:

    # "Lisa had made chicken fried steak and mashed potatoes with gravy, along with creamed spinach and dinner rolls."
    "Lisa había hecho filete de pollo frito con puré de patatas y salsa, además de espinacas a la crema y panecillos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:307
translate spanish dinner2_a4109bc0:

    # "I'm not a big fan of spinach, but everything else looks delicious."
    "No soy muy fan de las espinacas, pero todo lo demás tiene una pinta deliciosa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:308
translate spanish dinner2_82b4d135:

    # ss "Thanks for cooking Mom. This is amazing!"
    ss "Gracias por cocinar, mamá. ¡Esto está increíble!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:309
translate spanish dinner2_132b8415:

    # sp "Amazing might be a strong word. [pcname] has been down in Brazil for the last three years. I bet they have some real amazing food down there, right?"
    sp "«Increíble» quizá sea una palabra demasiado fuerte. [pcname] lleva tres años en Brasil. Apuesto a que allí la comida es realmente increíble, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:316
translate spanish amazingtacos_d1df5759:

    # pc "No, she's right. These are perfect."
    pc "No, tiene razón. Están perfectos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:317
translate spanish amazingtacos_ac97708c:

    # pc "The food in Brazil was great, but there's something about a good homemade chicken fried steak that makes it really feel like I'm home again."
    pc "La comida en Brasil estaba buenísima, pero hay algo en un buen filete de pollo frito casero que me hace sentir de verdad como si estuviera de vuelta en casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:320
translate spanish amazingtacos_b2a06636:

    # sp "I'm glad you like it, and I'm glad that you're home."
    sp "Me alegro de que te guste y de que estés en casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:323
translate spanish mehtacos_bbafcb97:

    # pc "Yeah, this is nowhere near as good as the empanadas down there."
    pc "Sí, esto no se acerca ni de lejos a las empanadas de allí."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:326
translate spanish mehtacos_984cd73b:

    # sp "See, this is just cheap steak, breaded and fried. Not exactly gourmet cooking."
    sp "Mira, esto es solo filete barato, empanado y frito. No es precisamente cocina gourmet."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:327
translate spanish mehtacos_b89e34ff:

    # "Suzy glared at me and shook her head."
    "Suzy me miró con el ceño fruncido y negó con la cabeza."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:332
translate spanish dinner3_e9cd228e:

    # ss "So why are you back anyways?"
    ss "¿Y por qué has vuelto, de todos modos?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:335
translate spanish dinner3_900dc08e:

    # sp "Be nice."
    sp "Sé amable."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:336
translate spanish dinner3_ed0bffd1:

    # ss "I am being nice. It's just a question."
    ss "Estoy siendo amable. Solo es una pregunta."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:337
translate spanish dinner3_d0083d8d:

    # pc "I came back to help find my dad."
    pc "He vuelto para ayudar a encontrar a mi padre."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:338
translate spanish dinner3_92f7529c:

    # ss "Well good luck with that. He ran off with another woman. If he wanted to be found, we would've already found him."
    ss "Pues buena suerte con eso. Se fugó con otra mujer. Si quisiera que lo encontráramos, ya lo habríamos encontrado."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:341
translate spanish dinner3_06a83c9b:

    # sp "Stop."
    sp "Para."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:342
translate spanish dinner3_447f8572:

    # sp "Don't talk about him like that. Just stop."
    sp "No hables así de él. Para ya."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:343
translate spanish dinner3_95ae9b92:

    # ss "Sorry Mom."
    ss "Lo siento, mamá."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:346
translate spanish dinner3_d95dc3cd:

    # sp "I don't want to argue at the table. Let's just have a nice dinner and we can talk about your father tomorrow."
    sp "No quiero discutir en la mesa. Disfrutemos de una buena cena y ya hablaremos de tu padre mañana."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:347
translate spanish dinner3_74555258:

    # "We sit in silence for a few minutes, eating, not saying anything. "
    "Nos quedamos en silencio unos minutos, comiendo, sin decir nada. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:348
translate spanish dinner3_9ecbea22:

    # "I want to ask more. I want to know why she thought my dad would have run off with another woman. But Lisa is obviously upset, and I don't want to start a fight. "
    "Quiero preguntar más. Quiero saber por qué pensó que mi padre se habría fugado con otra mujer. Pero Lisa está claramente molesta y no quiero empezar una pelea. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:351
translate spanish dinner3_f1c7cb27:

    # sp "How long are you planning on staying, [pcname]?"
    sp "¿Cuánto tiempo piensas quedarte, [pcname]?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:352
translate spanish dinner3_ab1f2008:

    # pc "I'm back permanently. "
    pc "He vuelto para quedarme. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:353
translate spanish dinner3_2441805f:

    # sp "What? You're not going back to school? "
    sp "¿Qué? ¿No vas a volver a la universidad? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:354
translate spanish dinner3_4f22cfa1:

    # pc "I can't. The scholarship was for four years, but if I miss any time, the scholarship is revoked. School started two days ago. I won't be able to go back. "
    pc "No puedo. La beca era para cuatro años, pero si falto algún tiempo, me la retiran. Las clases empezaron hace dos días. No podré volver. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:356
translate spanish dinner3_eb965744:

    # sp "Oh no! I wouldn't have wanted you to come if I'd known that! Your father wouldn't have wanted you to give up school to help find him either!"
    sp "¡Oh, no! ¡No habría querido que vinieras si lo hubiera sabido! ¡Tu padre tampoco habría querido que dejaras la universidad para ayudar a encontrarlo!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:357
translate spanish dinner3_3c14b8e8:

    # pc "It's done. I wanted to come back. I wasn't doing great at school anyways. I'm not sure I would've made it through the next year. "
    pc "Ya está hecho. Yo quería volver. De todos modos, no me iba muy bien en la universidad. No estoy seguro de si habría aguantado el próximo curso. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:358
translate spanish dinner3_f36256a6:

    # sp "So what are you going to do then? "
    sp "¿Y qué vas a hacer entonces? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:359
translate spanish dinner3_e26eb0c6:

    # pc "I'll go to school here. Finish up my degree and get a job here. That way I can help you out and try to find my dad. "
    pc "Iré a la universidad aquí. Terminaré la carrera y buscaré trabajo aquí. Así podré echarte una mano e intentar encontrar a mi padre. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:360
translate spanish dinner3_f98fa327:

    # "Lisa looks like she is about to cry. "
    "Lisa parece que está a punto de llorar. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:362
translate spanish dinner3_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/lisa_sorry2.wav'
    voice 'voices/lisa_sorry2.wav'

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:363
translate spanish dinner3_ce872a9f:

    # sp "I'm sorry you had to give all that up. I shouldn't have even sent that e-mail. "
    sp "Siento que hayas tenido que renunciar a todo eso. Ni siquiera debería haberte enviado ese correo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:364
translate spanish dinner3_f416188f:

    # pc "It's fine, really. I'm glad you sent it. I want to help, and I like being back. I didn't really have any friends down there. It's hard when you can barely speak the language. "
    pc "No pasa nada, de verdad. Me alegro de que lo enviaras. Quiero ayudar, y me gusta haber vuelto. La verdad es que no tenía amigos allí. Es difícil cuando apenas hablas el idioma. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:365
translate spanish dinner3_e31cfdde:

    # pc "And I missed my family. "
    pc "Y echaba de menos a mi familia. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:367
translate spanish dinner3_5f7f342a:

    # sp "We missed you too, right Suzy?"
    sp "Nosotras también te echábamos de menos, ¿verdad, Suzy?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:369
translate spanish dinner3_48c93c5d:

    # ss "Gag me. "
    ss "Qué asco. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:370
translate spanish dinner3_081c7332:

    # ss "If you're going to sign up for school, you better do it tomorrow. Registration is closing soon. "
    ss "Si vas a matricularte en la escuela, más vale que lo hagas mañana. El plazo de inscripción se acaba pronto. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:371
translate spanish dinner3_038c9ed9:

    # sp "She's right. Suzy, you can give him a ride up to the school in the morning so he can get everything straightened out. "
    sp "Tiene razón. Suzy, puedes llevarlo a la escuela por la mañana para que pueda arreglar todo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:373
translate spanish dinner3_c0cf4e1c:

    # ss "Why do I have to give him a ride? "
    ss "¿Por qué tengo que llevarlo yo? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:374
translate spanish dinner3_31d1c1eb:

    # sp "Because I have to work and [pcname] just got back to town and doesn't have a car."
    sp "Porque yo tengo que trabajar y [pcname] acaba de volver a la ciudad y no tiene coche."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:375
translate spanish dinner3_c6d0a215:

    # sp "AND because I asked you to. "
    sp "Y porque te lo he pedido. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:377
translate spanish dinner3_7197e500:

    # ss "Okay, fine. Be ready to go at 10 a.m. though. If you're not ready, I'm not taking you. "
    ss "Vale, está bien. Pero tenlo todo listo para salir a las 10 de la mañana. Si no estás listo, no te llevo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:378
translate spanish dinner3_b0883318:

    # sp "Show him around town too. It's been a while since he's been here."
    sp "Enséñale también la ciudad. Hace tiempo que no viene por aquí."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:379
translate spanish dinner3_a6b45ae3:

    # ss "Fine, but you need to get a car fast, because I can't be your chauffeur all the time. I have a life, you know."
    ss "Vale, pero tienes que conseguir un coche pronto, porque no puedo hacer de chófer todo el tiempo. Tengo mi vida, ya sabes."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:380
translate spanish dinner3_9083962a:

    # pc "You're right. I need to get a car. I need a cell phone too. So I need a job."
    pc "Tienes razón. Necesito un coche. También necesito un móvil. Así que necesito un trabajo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:382
translate spanish dinner3_4bee5430:

    # sp "What happened to your cell phone?"
    sp "¿Qué te ha pasado con el móvil?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:383
translate spanish dinner3_0e7d850c:

    # pc "I sort of forgot it in Brazil."
    pc "Se me quedó olvidado en Brasil."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:384
translate spanish dinner3_fcf63dc9:

    # sp "Oh no!"
    sp "¡Oh, no!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:385
translate spanish dinner3_706f59f6:

    # pc "No big deal. I'll get another, but I need money for that."
    pc "No pasa nada. Me compraré otro, pero necesito dinero para eso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:386
translate spanish dinner3_fe6322c5:

    # sp "It seems they're always looking for administrative assistants at the law offices downtown. I'm sure you could do that, with how smart you are. "
    sp "Parece que siempre están buscando asistentes administrativos en los bufetes del centro. Seguro que podrías hacerlo, con lo lista que eres. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:388
translate spanish dinner3_b7e8d5cc:

    # ss "Who says he's so smart?"
    ss "¿Quién dice que es tan inteligente?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:389
translate spanish dinner3_905e17eb:

    # sp "He qualified for that college in Brazil on a full scholarship. "
    sp "Consiguió entrar en esa universidad de Brasil con una beca completa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:390
translate spanish dinner3_1232931d:

    # ss "Yeah, and then flunked out of it apparently. "
    ss "Sí, y luego, por lo que parece, lo echaron por suspender."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:392
translate spanish dinner3_9a859b5f:

    # sp "Be nice! "
    sp "¡Sé amable!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:393
translate spanish dinner3_eac3f948:

    # "Suzy rolls her eyes. "
    "Suzy pone los ojos en blanco."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:395
translate spanish dinner3_cd1c0018:

    # sp "Anyway, I was going to say, you could use your father's car, if we could find the key."
    sp "En fin, iba a decir que podrías usar el coche de tu padre, si encontráramos la llave."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:396
translate spanish dinner3_fb35da6b:

    # sp "I'm not sure where he put it. I couldn't find it in his dresser and I didn't touch much down in the basement before the police locked it up."
    sp "No sé muy bien dónde la dejó. No la encontré en su cómoda y no revisé mucho el sótano antes de que la policía lo precintara."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:397
translate spanish dinner3_602ba288:

    # sp "I haven't even seen him drive it in at least a month."
    sp "Ni siquiera le he visto conducirlo en al menos un mes."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:398
translate spanish dinner3_3c301d5a:

    # pc "Okay, I'll check it out sometime."
    pc "Vale, lo miraré en algún momento."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:401
translate spanish dinner3_3dbf05d8:

    # ss "I'm done. I'm going up to my room."
    ss "Ya he terminado. Me voy a mi habitación."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:402
translate spanish dinner3_f3968cc8:

    # ss "Be ready at 10 tomorrow [bro]."
    ss "Tenlo todo listo para mañana a las 10 [bro]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:403
translate spanish dinner3_0da1b457:

    # "With that she rushes out of the dining room and up the stairs. "
    "Dicho esto, sale corriendo del comedor y sube las escaleras. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:406
translate spanish dinner3_e9cab60e:

    # sp "You'll have to excuse her. She's probably just going to talk to her boyfriend."
    sp "Tendrás que disculparla. Probablemente solo vaya a hablar con su novio."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:407
translate spanish dinner3_3a98b7ff:

    # sp "She does this almost every night. He lives in Whiterock and they hardly ever get to see each other anymore, so they talk on the phone a lot. "
    sp "Hace esto casi todas las noches. Él vive en Whiterock y ya casi nunca se ven, así que hablan mucho por teléfono. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:408
translate spanish dinner3_c969083e:

    # sp "Try to get along with her, okay?"
    sp "Intenta llevarte bien con ella, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:409
translate spanish dinner3_cfc6d9f8:

    # sp "She may not show it, but she is really upset over your father. She loves him and misses him too. "
    sp "Puede que no lo demuestre, pero está muy afectada por lo de tu padre. Le quiere y también le echa de menos. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:410
translate spanish dinner3_856a2ed5:

    # sp "And even though she'd probably never tell you, I know she missed you as well. "
    sp "Y aunque probablemente nunca te lo diría, sé que también te echaba de menos a ti. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:411
translate spanish dinner3_54567235:

    # sp "She was different after you left. Quieter and sullen. Lonely, I think. "
    sp "Estaba diferente después de que te fueras. Más callada y taciturna. Solitaria, creo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:412
translate spanish dinner3_02d1dafd:

    # sp "I know you two didn't hang out much, but I think she liked that you were always there to have her back. When you left, I think she felt a little abandoned. "
    sp "Sé que vosotros dos no pasabais mucho tiempo juntos, pero creo que a ella le gustaba que siempre estuvieras ahí para apoyarla. Cuando te fuiste, creo que se sintió un poco abandonada. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:413
translate spanish dinner3_2aec8af1:

    # "I never thought about that really. I didn't have a close relationship with Suzy, but we didn't fight really either. I was mad at my dad when I left, and resentful towards Lisa and Suzy for taking him away from me. "
    "Nunca lo había pensado así. No tenía una relación muy cercana con Suzy, pero tampoco es que nos peleáramos. Estaba enfadada con mi padre cuando me fui, y resentida con Lisa y Suzy por habérmelo quitado. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:414
translate spanish dinner3_9b39d1de:

    # "I never really gave them a chance. "
    "Nunca les di una oportunidad. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:415
translate spanish dinner3_4270ba94:

    # pc "I'm sorry for how I acted before I left. I've done a lot of growing up since then. I shouldn't have treated you and Suzy like I did. "
    pc "Siento cómo me comporté antes de irme. He madurado mucho desde entonces. No debería haberte tratado a ti y a Suzy como lo hice. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:417
translate spanish dinner3_f468cec8:

    # sp "Oh, you are beyond forgiven. You were a teenager. I get it. "
    sp "Oh, estás más que perdonada. Eras una adolescente. Lo entiendo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:418
translate spanish dinner3_e1c5605f:

    # sp "Your dad understood too. He was never upset at you. "
    sp "Tu padre también lo entendía. Nunca se enfadó contigo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:419
translate spanish dinner3_983990a9:

    # pc "I wish he was here. "
    pc "Ojalá estuviera aquí. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:421
translate spanish dinner3_b9c6a980:

    # sp "Me too."
    sp "Yo también."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:424
translate spanish dinner3_f2041521:

    # "I stand up next to her and give her a hug, holding her close. "
    "Me levanto y me acerco a ella para darle un abrazo, abrazándola con fuerza. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:426
translate spanish dinner3_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/lisa_iloveyou2.wav'
    voice 'voices/lisa_iloveyou2.wav'

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:427
translate spanish dinner3_dbd4b8fb:

    # sp "I love you."
    sp "Te quiero."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:428
translate spanish dinner3_931fdb2e:

    # pc "I love you too, Lisa."
    pc "Yo también te quiero, Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:430
translate spanish dishes_90fef3a5:

    # pc "I'll get the dishes, okay?"
    pc "Yo me encargo de los platos, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:431
translate spanish dishes_cdac8c69:

    # sp "Oh you don't have to do that. I'll get them."
    sp "Oh, no hace falta que lo hagas. Yo me encargo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:432
translate spanish dishes_8c3d6761:

    # pc "It's okay. You fed me, it's the least I can do."
    pc "No pasa nada. Me has dado de comer, es lo menos que puedo hacer."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:435
translate spanish dishes_631bfdab:

    # "I pick up the empty plates from the table and carry them into the kitchen, setting them into the sink."
    "Recojo los platos vacíos de la mesa y los llevo a la cocina, dejándolos en el fregadero."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:438
translate spanish dishes_96b0df67:

    # "Then I start washing dishes while she puts what little leftovers there are into storage containers and into the refrigerator."
    "Luego empiezo a fregar los platos mientras ella guarda las pocas sobras que quedan en recipientes y las mete en la nevera."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:439
translate spanish dishes_9d9933cd:

    # sp "You don't have to do all of them, [pcname]. Some of those dishes are from a few days ago."
    sp "No tienes que fregarlos todos, [pcname]. Algunos de esos platos son de hace unos días."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:440
translate spanish dishes_e9dbfb00:

    # pc "It's no problem, really. I don't mind."
    pc "No hay problema, de verdad. No me importa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:441
translate spanish dishes_92402374:

    # "I scrub the dishes and put them away into the dishwasher. She's right. It seems the dishes have been piling in the sink for a few days. It's mostly coffee cups and silverware though."
    "Fregó los platos y los metió en el lavavajillas. Tiene razón. Parece que los platos llevan varios días acumulándose en el fregadero. Aunque son sobre todo tazas de café y cubiertos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:442
translate spanish dishes_e91f1694:

    # "While I do the dishes, Lisa wipes off the counter and the stove, then comes over and stands next to me, watching and smiling."
    "Mientras yo fregaba los platos, Lisa limpió la encimera y la cocina, luego se acercó y se quedó a mi lado, observándome y sonriendo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:445
translate spanish dishes_688415e5:

    # sp "It's so great having you back home."
    sp "Es genial tenerte de vuelta en casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:446
translate spanish dishes_8ba74747:

    # sp "And not just to help out with the chores."
    sp "Y no solo para ayudar con las tareas domésticas."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:447
translate spanish dishes_be5f85fa:

    # sp "Look at you. You're all grown up now. You turned out to be such a great person."
    sp "Mírate. Ya eres toda una adulta. Te has convertido en una persona estupenda."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:448
translate spanish dishes_0621a10e:

    # sp "I'm proud of you, [pcname]."
    sp "Estoy orgullosa de ti, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:449
translate spanish dishes_419a081b:

    # pc "Thanks, Lisa."
    pc "Gracias, Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:450
translate spanish dishes_2e22a4be:

    # sp "You don't have to call me by my first name, you know."
    sp "No tienes por qué llamarme por mi nombre de pila, ¿sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:451
translate spanish dishes_49c20c2a:

    # sp "Isn't there something else you'd rather call me?"
    sp "¿No hay algún otro nombre con el que prefieras llamarme?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:464
translate spanish dishes_255098d6:

    # pc "I guess I could call you [mom]."
    pc "Supongo que podría llamarte [mom]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:465
translate spanish dishes_fe663261:

    # "She smiles and rubs my back with one hand."
    "Ella sonríe y me acaricia la espalda con una mano."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:466
translate spanish dishes_74fbfcd0:

    # sp "I like that."
    sp "Me gusta eso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:469
translate spanish notreadymom_1d99098b:

    # sp "I understand, but I hope you will be some day."
    sp "Lo entiendo, pero espero que algún día lo estés."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:474
translate spanish dishesdone_e3f22ce7:

    # "It only takes about ten minutes to finish the dishes, then I start the dishwasher and dry off my hands."
    "Solo tardo unos diez minutos en terminar de fregar los platos, luego pongo el lavavajillas y me seco las manos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:477
translate spanish dishesdone_0600f8f0:

    # sp "Thank you so much for the help."
    sp "Muchas gracias por la ayuda."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:478
translate spanish dishesdone_aaa5ef92:

    # pc "It's no problem at all. I'll try to help you more around the house too."
    pc "No hay ningún problema. Intentaré ayudarte más en casa también."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:479
translate spanish dishesdone_6d09b2a0:

    # sp "I could definitely use it. Between looking for your father and having to work all the time, I just don't seem to have enough time in the day."
    sp "Me vendría muy bien. Entre buscar a tu padre y tener que trabajar todo el tiempo, parece que no tengo suficientes horas al día."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:482
translate spanish bedtime_108b39c6:

    # pc "I'm getting pretty tired. I should probably go get ready for bed. It sounds like I have a big day tomorrow."
    pc "Estoy bastante cansada. Probablemente debería irme a preparar para acostarme. Parece que mañana me espera un día ajetreado."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:483
translate spanish bedtime_35fcb529:

    # sp "Oh you're right, it is getting late."
    sp "Oh, tienes razón, se está haciendo tarde."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:484
translate spanish bedtime_37eafefd:

    # sp "Your bed should be made up, but let me know if you need anything else."
    sp "Tu cama debería estar hecha, pero avísame si necesitas algo más."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:485
translate spanish bedtime_34bcfe10:

    # pc "I should be good. Thanks. "
    pc "Estaré bien. Gracias. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:486
translate spanish bedtime_39e280b3:

    # sp "You're welcome. Goodnight honey. "
    sp "De nada. Buenas noches, cariño. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:490
translate spanish bedtime_cb73fb79:

    # "I start walking up the stairs, but stop when she calls up after me."
    "Empiezo a subir las escaleras, pero me detengo cuando ella me llama."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:491
translate spanish bedtime_d7236e30:

    # sp "Hey."
    sp "Oye."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:493
translate spanish bedtime_ac8e7326:

    # sp "I'm so glad you're home. "
    sp "Me alegro mucho de que estés en casa. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:494
translate spanish bedtime_0e1f6f09:

    # pc "I'm glad to be home. "
    pc "Me alegro de estar en casa. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:495
translate spanish bedtime_c2eac4d5:

    # "And surprisingly, that is true. I had been nervous the entire way here, but now it is starting to feel like home again. I've missed this place and these people. "
    "Y, sorprendentemente, es verdad. He estado nerviosa todo el camino hasta aquí, pero ahora empiezo a sentirme como en casa otra vez. He echado de menos este lugar y a esta gente. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:496
translate spanish bedtime_8988551c:

    # "And I am excited to get my life started again. "
    "Y estoy emocionada por volver a empezar mi vida. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:499
translate spanish bedtime_a9cb4b72:

    # "I walk up and go into my bedroom, closing the door behind me."
    "Subo y entro en mi habitación, cerrando la puerta detrás de mí."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:502
translate spanish bedtime_34780e18:

    # "I can't help but think of all the things that I need to do."
    "No puedo evitar pensar en todas las cosas que tengo que hacer."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:503
translate spanish bedtime_78eef5f3:

    # "Register for college, find a job, get a car, get a phone. "
    "Matricularme en la universidad, encontrar un trabajo, conseguir un coche, conseguir un teléfono. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:504
translate spanish bedtime_733bb6e8:

    # "And maybe most important of all, I need to find out what happened to my dad."
    "Y quizá lo más importante de todo, necesito averiguar qué le pasó a mi padre."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:505
translate spanish bedtime_dea2a7f7:

    # "Something catches my attention from the corner of my eye. There is a clear view between my window and the window in the house next door. Jamie's window. "
    "Algo me llama la atención por el rabillo del ojo. Hay una vista despejada entre mi ventana y la ventana de la casa de al lado. La ventana de Jamie. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:509
translate spanish bedtime_2b3df239:

    # "Her curtains are open, and I see her moving around in her bedroom."
    "Tiene las cortinas abiertas y la veo moviéndose por su habitación."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:510
translate spanish bedtime_d26fe3f6:

    # "She is dressed for bed and dancing a little to some music that I can't hear. "
    "Lleva ropa de dormir y está bailando un poco al son de una música que no puedo oír. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:517
translate spanish keepwatchingjamie0_b1acde04:

    # "I stand there watching. This isn't the first time that this had happened. I remember back when I was a teenager, watching her through this same window."
    "Me quedo allí mirando. No es la primera vez que pasa esto. Recuerdo que, cuando era adolescente, la observaba a través de esta misma ventana."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:518
translate spanish keepwatchingjamie0_829b69aa:

    # "Sometimes I could catch quite the show."
    "A veces me tocaba ver todo un espectáculo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:519
translate spanish keepwatchingjamie0_f4cd189f:

    # "She dances around a little longer, looking quite nice in her t-shirt and short shorts."
    "Baila un rato más, muy mona con su camiseta y sus pantalones cortos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:522
translate spanish keepwatchingjamie0_a9d11f9b:

    # "Then she looks right up at me. I am caught!"
    "Entonces me mira directamente. ¡Me ha pillado!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:523
translate spanish keepwatchingjamie0_416b1742:

    # "I start to turn around, pretend that I hadn't seen anything. That I hadn't been watching."
    "Empiezo a dar media vuelta, fingiendo que no he visto nada. Que no la estaba mirando."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:526
translate spanish keepwatchingjamie0_015e93e4:

    # "But she just smiles and waves."
    "Pero ella solo sonríe y me saluda con la mano."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:527
translate spanish keepwatchingjamie0_4f3a3ee4:

    # "I wave back."
    "Le devuelvo el saludo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:530
translate spanish keepwatchingjamie0_47c7c917:

    # "Then she walks over to the window and closes the curtain."
    "Luego se acerca a la ventana y cierra la cortina."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:531
translate spanish keepwatchingjamie0_a0ca000d:

    # "Show's over folks, time to go to bed."
    "Se acabó el espectáculo, amigos, hora de irse a la cama."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:536
translate spanish stopwatchingjamie0_9d8f3e71:

    # "I shouldn't be watching. That's a pretty creepy thing to do."
    "No debería estar mirando. Es algo bastante espeluznante."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:537
translate spanish stopwatchingjamie0_157d17b0:

    # "I turn away and try not to think about what I might be missing."
    "Me doy la vuelta e intento no pensar en lo que me estoy perdiendo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:540
translate spanish getreadyforbed_e8de2125:

    # "I take my toothbrush from my suitcase and open the door that leads into the bathroom between Suzy's room and my room."
    "Saco el cepillo de dientes de la maleta y abro la puerta que da al baño, entre la habitación de Suzy y la mía."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:543
translate spanish getreadyforbed_758405dc:

    # "The door that leads into her bedroom is open and I see her lying on the bed in her night clothes, talking into her cell phone. "
    "La puerta de su dormitorio está abierta y la veo tumbada en la cama en pijama, hablando por el móvil. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:545
translate spanish getreadyforbed_d1f1872b:

    # "She gives me an annoyed look."
    "Me lanza una mirada molesta."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:547
translate spanish getreadyforbed_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/suzy_day0_1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/suzy_day0_1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:548
translate spanish getreadyforbed_9fef9570:

    # ss "Ugh! Are you going to shut the door or just stand there staring at me like a pervert?"
    ss "¡Uf! ¿Vas a cerrar la puerta o te vas a quedar ahí mirándome como un pervertido?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:549
translate spanish getreadyforbed_b2395364:

    # pc "Sorry."
    pc "Lo siento."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:552
translate spanish getreadyforbed_1698b2b6:

    # "I shut the door quickly, giving both of us our privacy."
    "Cierro la puerta rápidamente, dándonos a ambas un poco de intimidad."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:553
translate spanish getreadyforbed_44d2215b:

    # "This is going to take some getting used to."
    "Me va a costar acostumbrarme a esto."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:554
translate spanish getreadyforbed_3e0e7e7e:

    # "I turn to the sink. It is all covered with her things."
    "Me dirijo al lavabo. Está todo cubierto con sus cosas."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:555
translate spanish getreadyforbed_6c8adbe6:

    # "I find the toothpaste among the clutter of hair products and makeup and brush my teeth, then clear out a place for me to keep my toothbrush."
    "Encuentro la pasta de dientes entre el desorden de productos para el pelo y maquillaje, me lavo los dientes y luego hago un hueco para guardar mi cepillo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:556
translate spanish getreadyforbed_ccb610d3:

    # "I've been gone for three years. I hate to just come back and force her to make room for me, but I am going to need some space in here as well if we have to share this bathroom."
    "He estado fuera tres años. No me gusta volver y obligarla a hacerme un hueco, pero voy a necesitar algo de espacio aquí también si tenemos que compartir este baño."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:557
translate spanish getreadyforbed_fbfe7d80:

    # "With that done, I head to bed."
    "Una vez hecho esto, me voy a la cama."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:560
translate spanish getreadyforbed_ce296358:

    # "The bed is soft. Even more so than I remember. And the sheets smell like home."
    "La cama es mullida. Incluso más de lo que recordaba. Y las sábanas huelen a hogar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:561
translate spanish getreadyforbed_ada2c3fb:

    # "All of this just feels so comforting. It is strange. At first, I had been worried that you could never go home again. That this would all be too different, and I wouldn't fit in here anymore. "
    "Todo esto me resulta tan reconfortante. Es extraño. Al principio, me preocupaba que nunca pudieras volver a casa. Que todo esto fuera demasiado diferente y que ya no encajara aquí. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:562
translate spanish getreadyforbed_639a54c3:

    # "Now though. Now I feel good about all of it. I feel like I am home for the first time in a long time."
    "Pero ahora. Ahora me siento bien con todo esto. Siento que estoy en casa por primera vez en mucho tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:563
translate spanish getreadyforbed_f4f9d6d2:

    # "Just one thing is missing – Dad."
    "Solo falta una cosa: papá."

